So, let's let them talk as sisters first

566
00:43:57,540 --> 00:44:00,540
Miss Blue seems upset about something.

567
00:44:01,540 --> 00:44:04,020
You can tell us.

568
00:44:04,220 --> 00:44:06,300
We are ready to help you.

569
00:44:07,460 --> 00:44:09,940
If it's something personal that you don't dare tell others about,

570
00:44:10,180 --> 00:44:11,660
You can tell us about it too.

571
00:44:11,660 --> 00:44:14,180
We promise we'll keep the secret.

572
00:44:21,420 --> 00:44:25,860
In your opinion,

573
00:44:27,500 --> 00:44:30,700
What is love?

574
00:44:34,860 --> 00:44:36,300
For me,

575
00:44:36,940 --> 00:44:39,660
Love is staying beside each other,

576
00:44:40,180 --> 00:44:42,420
And complement each other's shortcomings,

577
00:44:42,420 --> 00:44:44,420
Protect and care for each other,

578
00:44:45,140 --> 00:44:48,340
And to be each other's happiness on ordinary days.

579
00:44:49,020 --> 00:44:51,900
This person is Sister Dean.

580
00:44:55,220 --> 00:44:56,860
For me,

581
00:44:58,100 --> 00:45:00,900
I believe in good love

582
00:45:00,900 --> 00:45:02,460
It makes us love ourselves

583
00:45:03,620 --> 00:45:06,900
In the past, I thought I could live well on my own

584
00:45:07,100 --> 00:45:08,660
Without relying on anyone

585
00:45:09,980 --> 00:45:12,860
But after I met Mrs. Nam

586
00:45:13,180 --> 00:45:14,540
I realized

587
00:45:14,780 --> 00:45:18,340
That we don't need to always be strong or perfect at everything

588
00:45:19,420 --> 00:45:22,580
If one day I want to be weak or want to cry

589
00:45:22,820 --> 00:45:26,020
Mrs. Nam will always be by my side to support me

590
00:45:28,220 --> 00:45:29,180
if

591
00:45:29,580 --> 00:45:31,580
What do you think love is, Miss Blue?

592
00:45:35,580 --> 00:45:37,660
I don't know

593
00:45:38,780 --> 00:45:40,740
I've never experienced love before

594
00:45:42,100 --> 00:45:43,780
my love

595
00:45:44,260 --> 00:45:46,900
It is limited to my love for the people of Madeleine

596
00:45:50,900 --> 00:45:52,860
As a princess

597
00:45:53,500 --> 00:45:55,420
I can only do my best to carry out my duties

598
00:45:56,700 --> 00:45:58,580
So I don't know

599
00:45:59,100 --> 00:46:02,780
This mutual love

600
00:46:04,340 --> 00:46:06,180
How does he feel?

601
00:46:11,900 --> 00:46:13,420
Don't worry too much

602
00:46:13,740 --> 00:46:17,300
When the time comes, you'll know

603
00:46:32,940 --> 00:46:36,020
[Normandy, France]

604
00:46:43,660 --> 00:46:45,300
Excuse me, are you Miss Fa?

605
00:46:48,460 --> 00:46:50,420
Welcome, please have a seat

606
00:46:54,980 --> 00:46:56,300
My name is Sebastian

607
00:46:56,620 --> 00:46:58,580
A close friend of Prince Karel

608
00:46:58,580 --> 00:47:01,060
I heard Princess Blue sent you here

609
00:47:02,020 --> 00:47:04,260
My name is Fa, and I am a Thai journalist

610
00:47:06,900 --> 00:47:09,020
Her Highness the Princess has a secret message

611
00:47:09,020 --> 00:47:11,260
I must deliver it to His Highness the Prince myself.

612
00:47:12,500 --> 00:47:14,180
How can I trust you?

613
00:47:20,260 --> 00:47:22,060
Can this prove my identity?

614
00:47:30,220 --> 00:47:31,700
Hello Sebastian.

615
00:47:31,700 --> 00:47:33,540
I'm Princess Blue.

616
00:47:33,860 --> 00:47:35,520
Fa one of us.

617
00:47:35,520 --> 00:47:38,340
I hope you trust everything she says.

618
00:47:38,900 --> 00:47:40,740
I want to ask you a favor.

619
00:47:41,140 --> 00:47:43,620
Please contact Karel secretly.

620
00:47:43,860 --> 00:47:45,180
Thank you very much.

621
00:47:57,860 --> 00:47:59,980
His Highness the Prince is coming to France.

622
00:48:01,660 --> 00:48:02,820
truly?

623
00:48:04,580 --> 00:48:06,900
When His Highness arrives, I will contact him immediately.

624
00:48:08,100 --> 00:48:09,460
Thank you very much.

625
00:48:09,700 --> 00:48:11,620
I will break the news to Thailand immediately.

626
00:48:11,620 --> 00:48:13,380
The princess will be very happy.

627
00:48:14,580 --> 00:48:18,260
Please keep this matter confidential.

628
00:49:40,860 --> 00:49:41,900
Is there still a long way to go?

629
00:49:44,500 --> 00:49:46,900
Once we get over this mountain, we will reach Thailand.

630
00:49:48,860 --> 00:49:51,060
I didn't expect that Mr. Henry would come by himself.

631
00:49:51,900 --> 00:49:53,740
Had I not faced these useless thieves,

632
00:49:54,140 --> 00:49:55,980
Why did I end up in this miserable situation?

633
00:49:57,540 --> 00:49:59,100
The weapons I asked you to equip,

634
00:49:59,460 --> 00:50:00,540
Did you bring it all?

635
00:50:01,860 --> 00:50:02,860
I brought it all.

636
00:50:03,180 --> 00:50:04,140
Good.

637
00:50:17,740 --> 00:50:21,220
[Fanthwarth Hospital]

638
00:50:31,340 --> 00:50:32,180
my dad.

639
00:50:41,780 --> 00:50:42,820
How are you, my daughter?

640
00:50:43,500 --> 00:50:44,740
I'm much better.

641
00:50:45,100 --> 00:50:47,020
I am waiting for the doctor to notify me when I will be discharged from the hospital.

642
00:50:48,620 --> 00:50:49,460
Where is the princess?

643
00:50:50,500 --> 00:50:51,700
She's taking a shower.

644
00:50:57,180 --> 00:50:59,140
Dad, did something happen?

645
00:51:01,580 --> 00:51:03,780
These criminals we eliminated on the island,

646
00:51:04,820 --> 00:51:05,900
They are all Thai.

647
00:51:08,700 --> 00:51:11,420
So I think they were hired by someone.

648
00:51:12,220 --> 00:51:14,140
I've ordered my men to investigate now.

649
00:51:14,620 --> 00:51:16,380
To see if there are any other gangs.

650
00:51:16,940 --> 00:51:19,020
-So I think... -Dad, don't you find it strange?

651
00:51:20,020 --> 00:51:23,460
Why were the criminals able to find me and Miss Blue so quickly?

652
00:51:26,220 --> 00:51:27,500
What do you mean?

653
00:51:51,460 --> 00:51:52,380
I am waiting

654
00:52:00,460 --> 00:52:01,340
It's okay now

655
00:52:01,580 --> 00:52:02,460
Thank you very much

656
00:52:22,420 --> 00:52:25,260
[VIP Room 3111]

657
00:53:24,580 --> 00:53:25,020
[emergency corridor]

658
00:54:08,340 --> 00:54:09,300
It's me

659
00:54:10,700 --> 00:54:12,140
Hide here first

660
00:54:12,380 --> 00:54:13,860
I'll take care of the rest

661
00:54:29,140 --> 00:54:30,860
Commander!

662
00:54:34,820 --> 00:54:36,020
Don't mind me

663
00:54:37,180 --> 00:54:39,380
That person fled there, they rushed and chased him.

664
00:54:39,580 --> 00:54:40,660
Hurry up!

665
00:54:41,260 --> 00:54:42,140
Let's go.

666
00:55:01,300 --> 00:55:02,660
The road outside is now clear.

667
00:55:02,940 --> 00:55:04,660
How did the police know I was here?

668
00:55:05,780 --> 00:55:06,900
I don't know either.

669
00:55:07,740 --> 00:55:10,500
You must escape as quickly as possible before Waithet sends his men to block the hospital's exits.

670
00:55:11,060 --> 00:55:14,460
Run away as quickly as possible.

671
00:55:15,380 --> 00:55:16,780
Listen to me carefully.

672
00:55:17,580 --> 00:55:19,020
If I don't survive,

673
00:55:19,500 --> 00:55:20,620
You won't survive either.

674
00:55:53,900 --> 00:55:55,420
Dad, aren't you suspicious?

675
00:55:55,660 --> 00:55:59,300
How did the criminals find me and Miss Blue so quickly?

676
00:55:59,580 --> 00:56:00,980
What do you mean?

677
00:56:00,980 --> 00:56:03,700
Is Commander Santi with you on the same mission?

678
00:56:03,980 --> 00:56:05,540
Are you trying to say?

679
00:56:06,380 --> 00:56:08,260
That Santi is in cahoots with the gang?

680
00:56:08,900 --> 00:56:11,140
Dad, we can't trust anyone now.

681
00:56:11,140 --> 00:56:13,620
There are people who follow Madeleine and are infiltrated in the police team.

682
00:56:13,900 --> 00:56:15,260
You have received an emergency summons.

683
00:56:15,260 --> 00:56:16,500
I have to go to the hotel immediately.

684
00:56:16,500 --> 00:56:18,420
The princess's safety is your responsibility now

685
00:56:18,700 --> 00:56:20,140
No one told me

686
00:56:20,380 --> 00:56:21,700
Did the commander tell you that?

687
00:56:22,420 --> 00:56:23,780
Nothing, let's stay like this for now

688
00:56:24,420 --> 00:56:26,580
Sister Dean, it's not that I don't trust my father

689
00:56:26,580 --> 00:56:27,780
But the police station

690
00:56:27,780 --> 00:56:30,020
The people around him, his men

691
00:56:30,020 --> 00:56:31,540
I don't trust any of them

692
00:56:33,580 --> 00:56:35,340
Your Highness, we have been ambushed

693
00:56:36,740 --> 00:56:39,220
They ambushed us, just as you expected

694
00:56:39,660 --> 00:56:41,660
I'll send some men to the island to prepare first

695
00:56:42,300 --> 00:56:44,300
Surely they will follow us to the island tomorrow

696
00:56:44,420 --> 00:56:45,700
Let me talk to Yod

697
00:56:45,700 --> 00:56:46,540
Good

698
00:56:51,060 --> 00:56:51,980
Sir

699
00:56:55,260 --> 00:56:57,700
Looks like I wasn't wrong, it's really you, Commander

700
00:56:58,180 --> 00:57:00,340
I'll give you two options

701
00:57:01,020 --> 00:57:02,620
Either help the police

702
00:57:03,340 --> 00:57:04,620
Or you choose to go to prison

703
00:57:21,660 --> 00:57:22,860
Sister Nam, how are you?

704
00:57:22,860 --> 00:57:23,740
Are you well?

705
00:57:24,860 --> 00:57:26,940
Fortunately we got Miss Blue out in time

706
00:57:27,460 --> 00:57:29,020
Did you catch him?

707
00:57:29,820 --> 00:57:30,700
no

708
00:57:31,140 --> 00:57:32,220
He ran away

709
00:57:33,700 --> 00:57:36,420
But Uncle Wathi now ordered a check

710
00:57:36,420 --> 00:57:38,420
From all surveillance footage at the exits of Surat Thani city

711
00:57:48,140 --> 00:57:49,020
It's okay now

712
00:57:49,220 --> 00:57:50,100
Thank you very much

713
00:58:22,900 --> 00:58:24,140
Your Highness, please wait a moment.

714
00:58:33,620 --> 00:58:35,500
We have arranged a car to take you to your accommodation in Khao Yai.

715
00:58:36,700 --> 00:58:37,780
Thanks.

716
00:58:38,580 --> 00:58:39,500
Take this.

717
00:58:40,380 --> 00:58:41,700
These are clothes that Fei prepared for you.

718
00:58:42,260 --> 00:58:43,540
I will inform you of any updates immediately.

719
00:58:49,980 --> 00:58:51,060
The car arrived.

720
00:58:54,780 --> 00:58:56,580
Are we leaving in this car?

721
00:58:57,660 --> 00:58:58,580
Yes, Your Highness.

722
00:58:58,860 --> 00:59:00,140
that way,

723
00:59:00,460 --> 00:59:02,140
The bad guys won't notice us.

724
00:59:05,420 --> 00:59:07,100
Rescue cars have arrived.

725
00:59:09,780 --> 00:59:12,140
At least there won't be corpses.

726
00:59:13,180 --> 00:59:14,700
Do you mean he was there before?

727
00:59:17,300 --> 00:59:18,500
I can't say for sure.

728
00:59:21,460 --> 00:59:22,380
Let's hurry.

729
00:59:22,940 --> 00:59:24,060
Your Highness, please.

730
00:59:25,060 --> 00:59:25,860
Let's go.

731
00:59:34,100 --> 00:59:36,700
[Khao Yai National Park]

732
00:59:48,620 --> 00:59:49,660
We have arrived.

733
00:59:51,980 --> 00:59:54,300
I didn't expect there to be a house hidden in the middle of the forest.

734
00:59:55,500 --> 00:59:57,260
There is no cell phone signal here.

735
00:59:57,260 --> 00:59:58,500
But if anything happens,

736
00:59:58,500 --> 01:00:01,220
Resort staff will fire a signal grenade to send a message.

737
01:00:02,140 --> 01:00:03,020
Help yourself.

738
01:00:22,660 --> 01:00:24,380
Any news about that policeman?

739
01:00:25,380 --> 01:00:27,020
My men are doing their best to track him down.

740
01:00:27,780 --> 01:00:30,060
But Team Watheit has been watching us closely lately.

741
01:00:31,420 --> 01:00:32,980
We have to wait a little while.

742
01:00:33,460 --> 01:00:34,780
I don't want to risk it.

743
01:00:41,940 --> 01:00:43,980
The reward is double the previous time.

744
01:00:44,620 --> 01:00:46,300
In exchange for you finding me within three days

745
01:00:49,620 --> 01:00:50,940
Vaio's place.

746
01:01:06,500 --> 01:01:07,780
I will send you the news.

747
01:01:32,300 --> 01:01:33,780
Miss Blue, did you sleep well?

748
01:01:34,540 --> 01:01:36,300
Yes, it was very comfortable.

749
01:01:37,100 --> 01:01:39,220
So, take a break now.

750
01:01:39,380 --> 01:01:41,460
I'll go prepare the food and I'll call you when I'm done.

751
01:01:42,740 --> 01:01:44,300
Ah, Miss Faio.

752
01:01:45,300 --> 01:01:46,100
Hmm.

753
01:01:48,020 --> 01:01:49,420
I have a question.

754
01:01:50,340 --> 01:01:51,140
Help yourself.

755
01:01:52,540 --> 01:01:55,500
Promise me first that you won't lie.

756
01:01:57,580 --> 01:01:59,300
Well, I promise I won't deceive you.

757
01:02:03,260 --> 01:02:05,700
Bua said you like me.

758
01:02:10,660 --> 01:02:11,660
ah...

759
01:02:11,660 --> 01:02:14,980
But I won't believe it until you say it yourself.

760
01:02:18,020 --> 01:02:21,380
Why are you asking this question suddenly?

761
01:02:24,620 --> 01:02:26,660
What are your feelings towards me?

762
01:02:32,020 --> 01:02:33,220
I...

763
01:02:35,140 --> 01:02:37,220
If my question is not appropriate...

764
01:02:37,540 --> 01:02:39,580
Then I hope you don't care either

765
01:02:47,980 --> 01:02:50,060
Not so, Miss Blue

766
01:02:55,860 --> 01:02:58,740
Because the issue is not limited to mere admiration

767
01:03:01,580 --> 01:03:03,060
What do you mean?

768
01:03:16,540 --> 01:03:19,220
Maybe it's too early to say this

769
01:03:19,500 --> 01:03:21,860
After all, we haven't known each other that long

770
01:03:24,580 --> 01:03:26,820
But I trust my feelings a lot

771
01:03:29,620 --> 01:03:31,260
What are your feelings?

772
01:03:41,580 --> 01:03:43,660
Sorry, I've overstepped my bounds

773
01:03:43,900 --> 01:03:45,940
I was clearly not aware of my position

774
01:03:46,820 --> 01:03:50,340
Even though I repeatedly warned myself to stick to my limits

775
01:03:51,100 --> 01:03:53,060
But every time I get closer to you

776
01:03:54,740 --> 01:03:56,660
I can't suppress my feelings

777
01:04:00,980 --> 01:04:02,260
I love you

778
01:04:11,220 --> 01:04:13,860
How many times have you fallen in love?

779
01:04:17,660 --> 01:04:18,620
What?

780
01:04:21,420 --> 01:04:22,780
before

781
01:04:23,220 --> 01:04:25,420
You've had a lot of love relationships

782
01:04:26,180 --> 01:04:27,900
Various events

783
01:04:28,620 --> 01:04:30,380
It made us get closer to each other

784
01:04:33,060 --> 01:04:35,700
So I want you to remember carefully and be sure of your feelings

785
01:04:36,900 --> 01:04:38,460
Is this really love?

786
01:04:39,980 --> 01:04:41,260
Or just attachment?

787
01:04:45,060 --> 01:04:46,580
I'm very clear about my feelings

788
01:04:49,820 --> 01:04:51,620
I'm sure it's love

789
01:05:12,900 --> 01:05:14,340
If you like me

790
01:05:16,020 --> 01:05:18,020
I won't mind

791
01:05:20,980 --> 01:05:23,260
But I may not be able to feel the same way

792
01:06:05,860 --> 01:06:07,260
If you like me

793
01:06:08,980 --> 01:06:11,060
I won't mind

794
01:06:13,980 --> 01:06:16,340
But I may not be able to feel the same way

795
01:06:25,620 --> 01:06:27,260
As long as you don't mind

796
01:06:27,460 --> 01:06:29,620
And don't be angry about what I just said

797
01:06:30,260 --> 01:06:31,900
I will be very happy

798
01:06:35,820 --> 01:06:37,220
For me

799
01:06:38,420 --> 01:06:40,900
You are the last love of my life

800
01:06:48,020 --> 01:06:51,100
Whether my hope is disappointed or my wish comes true

801
01:07:40,300 --> 01:07:41,940
After completing the mission here

802
01:07:41,940 --> 01:07:43,660
Will we return to Madeleine?

803
01:07:43,820 --> 01:07:44,780
not yet

804
01:07:45,860 --> 01:07:49,020
We're going to Thailand to get rid of the real princess

805
01:07:50,300 --> 01:07:52,900
Didn't Henry go? Why should we go too?

806
01:07:54,420 --> 01:07:56,140
I don't trust him

807
01:07:56,580 --> 01:07:59,260
Henry holds no grudge against the royal family

808
01:07:59,980 --> 01:08:02,220
If he sides with the princess

809
01:08:02,740 --> 01:08:05,660
My entire plan to take revenge on the royal family will fail

810
01:08:09,700 --> 01:08:11,900
What grudge do you hold against the royal family?

811
01:08:14,780 --> 01:08:16,340
This doesn't concern you

812
01:08:17,620 --> 01:08:19,979
It is enough to play the role of the princess well

813
01:08:33,300 --> 01:09:13,140
[Announcement of the next episode]

814
01:08:33,700 --> 01:08:35,700
My father will trick Henry into coming here

815
01:08:35,700 --> 01:08:37,100
And arrest them all

816
01:08:37,420 --> 01:08:38,260
Ah!

817
01:08:40,380 --> 01:08:41,500
Miss Lum.

818
01:08:42,859 --> 01:08:44,380
Is Miss Blue safe?

819
01:08:45,100 --> 01:08:46,819
Miss Blue has been arrested.

820
01:08:46,819 --> 01:08:47,460
What?

821
01:08:47,460 --> 01:08:49,180
But Uncle Watheet is looking for someone...

822
01:08:49,180 --> 01:08:50,060
- I'll go save her. - I am waiting.

823
01:08:50,060 --> 01:08:51,300
calm.

824
01:08:51,300 --> 01:08:53,660
Will King Father and Karel come to Thailand?

825
01:08:53,660 --> 01:08:56,300
Before she took the throne

826
01:08:56,500 --> 01:08:58,939
Our family can get together and go for walks together

827
01:08:58,939 --> 01:09:00,899
Grace, things are starting to go against our plan

828
01:09:01,220 --> 01:09:03,380
If my father and the king knew the truth

829
01:09:03,700 --> 01:09:05,500
We will certainly face the death penalty

830
01:09:06,779 --> 01:09:08,220
You look a lot like me

831
01:09:17,020 --> 01:10:30,660
[To watch the full version exclusively on the iQiyi application and the iQ.com website, the only official approved platform]

832
01:09:38,380 --> 01:09:42,500
♪ I don't know which star he is ♪

833
01:09:42,500 --> 01:09:48,859
♪ Who guided me to meet you ♪

834
01:09:50,340 --> 01:09:54,580
♪ Or maybe it's fate ♪

835
01:09:54,580 --> 01:10:01,260
♪ That made us meet here ♪

836
01:10:02,060 --> 01:10:07,820
♪ You're like the breeze that carries me soaring ♪

837
01:10:07,820 --> 01:10:12,860
♪ No matter how high I fly, I won't be afraid ♪

838
01:10:12,860 --> 01:10:18,580
♪ Your presence is enough for me, and I don't want anything else ♪

839
01:10:18,580 --> 01:10:22,740
♪ As long as we're together, my heart will be filled with warmth ♪

840
01:10:22,740 --> 01:10:27,740
♪ You are all the meaning of my life ♪

